oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Ledger book of Dr. W. B. Holmes
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This is a ledger book of Dr. W. B. Holmes of Granville, Jackson County, Tennessee. Dr. Holmes' ledger begins with 1851 and goes to 1872. He indexes his patients in the front of the book and has individual entries of their accounts in the remainder. Also found in the ledger was a small advertisement piece used as a book mark.
